I smell love in the air and it stinks like rotten eggs....JUST JOKING~!

The days slowly are getting better. 
I find myself listening for God more often and the more I listen the more I am hear. 

Don't feel sorry for me because things are improving.

Nothing is perfect nor will it ever be. I am okay with that. 

Day by day I am looking for those little pieces of goodness that are going to get me through the bad. 

I will get over you one day, I will be happy one day, until then I am content dealing with the angst of being a teenager girl.

"Being grown up isn't half as fun as growing up; these are the best days of our lives."--The Ataris....if they are right . . . I have nothing to look forward to. 

Twas another SUCKY Thursday. I am sure you don't want to hear the gory details but entailed a lack of memory, a broken car, a touch, a girlfriend, me slipping, work


I want to rid my self of these thoughts. It isn't fair, but once again no one said it would be. 
There are so many things that I want to change, to alter. Moments in time that can't be mine and will forever be wanted. I don't think forever is a word I can use though because I have never had a forever. 

It would be easy to cuddle with someone now but I don't want to cuddle with someone, I want to cuddle with THE one.

I think this is a sad movie night....


It is so much to ask for just to be wanted?

Oh tonight was so much fun Madelyn. We have got to do it more often.
We went to target, which I thought was doomed from the first moment. Well he was there, but that's oaky because it was just so funny. We went to the BRA section. It was so akward but Madelyn made it SOO funny. I couldn't stop laughing. Then all the crazy conversations in the car ranging from speaking in tongues to those SPECIAL GUYS! 

I wish that I could have the strength of actually ask him to prom madelyn, I don't have the guts to let myself down. Plus the datebility book said to get chased and not do the chasing. Maybe I will just let the BMW guy chase me...right?
Why can't he just chase me?

Angie: Thank you Samm- I love you too. you know some of the deal-e-o...you know the adoration.


OH ANGIE HOW I WISH I DIDN'T. I saw that number three times today at work...it felt like it just kept popping out of no where and throwing me off. That adoration is a killer....i shouldn't adore anymore....because that's just sad.


p.s. my voice is ....gone

I realized today that I actually want most likely to succeed, i hope that isn't dorky...lol

we have the beach house narrowed down....we are ready to start getting down to buisness.

i ordered my senior pictures today...well my ma did....it wasn't that high....well THAT high....

I really do think boys stink because they mess us gals up like whoa....and it just isn't fair!

Today was the annual Canoe Trip for Dual Biology. I have always looked forward to this ever since my sister's did it. I loved it. It's defintly one of those highschool experinces that you dont' forget. It was exactly what the doctor ordered; a good relaxing day of fun and enjoyment. My canoe buddies were hilarious and Sarah at the front...we let me tell you she is one competitive gal. I had to steer the boat, which was pretty hilarious since I was the most educated canoer and yet I couldn't keep us exactly straight. BUT HEY WE DIDN'T RUN INTO ONE BANK WE WEREN'T SUPPOSED TO. Stepping into the mudd and playing around was great. Oh, how I wish I could do this about every month. Life is grand. Things are going well. WOO HOO

school sucks like whoa...
I hate it...I HATE IT!

I can't wait for it to end....how many more days?

3RD PERIOD IS THE WORSE! WHY DO STUPID PEOPLE HAVE TO BE IN THERE....

I  MISS MY FRIENDS....NOT ONLY THOSE AT COLLEGE BUT THOSE AROUND ME BECAUSE IT SEEMS LIKE THEY ARE GONE TOO. SOMETIMES I WONDER IF I STILL HAVE FRIENDS BECAUSE THEY ALL SEEM INDIFFRENT TO ME, AS IF THEY COULD CARE LESS




OH WHOA IS ME...HOW NO ONE CARES!

Worked today, work tommrow and the day after...lol....

Frances sucks...it kaes everyone razy and think they ahve to come stock up on food...I just want to yell at them to GET OUT OF FOODLION!

I get paid for NOT working on Labor Day...anyone who has been there a year gets four hours extra pay on holidays...tha's tyyt...not matter who you are!

I love Adam of Maroon 5's voice! It so seductive and coarse...I like it..I like it alot....

school isn't starting yet, I haven't even finished all those papers...I have to re read them, correct them and then re type them!




I want make you feel beautiful
I don't mind spending every day out on your corner in the pouring rain. 
Look for the girl with the broken smile. 
Ask her if she wants to stay a while. 
She will be loved.

I walked into the highschool today. I hated being there. I am scared.

 I didn't think I would be, but I hate it. 

I am afraid that I will have the worst year ever. 

But these are supposed to be the best days of our lives!

I want to get this year over with. 

Things already are turing out diffrently that I had imagined. 

Make this quick...painless.

So much for my happy ending.

I am the one everyone goes to for advice. I have no one to talk to. I don't even really understand why I am like this. I NEED to cry....I can feel the well of tears filling up behind my eyes. The pressure hurts. I don't want to be a senior. It's going to stink. I want happiness.

What if I found you know? I don't think it would make that much of a difference because I am awalys AT WORK! 30 hours this week. All work and no play...you know what they say!

I didn't go to the beach yesterday. I cried b.c. of that. I wanted to sooooo badly but my mom told me to cancel LAST MINUTE. Courtney and I went out instead, but it just wasn't as good.

I worked over 9 hours today...I hate that. I need to do it, but it's so blah. Everyone at work says I should date this guy Anthony. He is adorable, but young and inexperienced. It's hilarious, because we flirt endlessly, "Samm, your sweet as honey." lol, but he knows that it ain't happening...lol...


I am a senior. I will be a freshman in less than a year....AT COLLEGE. I can't wait till College!!!!!!!!!

I can't wait to visit my FRIENDS AT COLLEGE!!!

I was good the first part of the day. Some people just aggrivate me though. 

My boss at Food Lion was joking with me and calling me a goodie goodie and that no one ever wanted a goodie. I knew he was joking but it HURT.....because deep down, that's what I believe. The what ifs are slowly drownding out the voices of reason.

I am sad that all my old senior friends are gone. I want to be where they are. I want to start a new chapter. I want to leave everything and everyone behind. I don't want to be me anymore. I can be someone else if I really tried. 

Sometimes my heart starts to hurt. Physically, because of the emotional pull of it. It's so silly to want it. I was watching the Prince and Me, and most people would think that the part that made me feel the most physical warmth and happiness would be the end. Instead, the part that I felt the most, the part I kept repeating, was the part when he reaches out and holds her hand. He plays with her hand. What's up with that....so simple....yet....


I have so many emotions, I would think I am pmsing, but I'm not....I don't know what I am going to do tommorow with both my uncle and mom bossing me around having me **FETCH**....i may lose my cool easy....although I don't really want too.

You wanna know more, more, more about me 
Gotta know reverse phsychology 
I'm the reason why you can't get to sleep 
I'm the girl you never get just quite what you see 

Hey! Hey! Hey! 

Could you see I want you by the way I push you away, Ya! 
Don't judge me tomorrow by the way I'm acting today 
Mix the words up with the actions do it all for your reaction Ya! 
Hey! Hey! 
Get tangled up in me 

You think that you know me 
You think that I'm only 
When everything I do is only to get tangled up in you 
You wanna know more, more, more about me 
I'm the girl that's sweeping you off your feet

It's one of those times where you have so much inside you, you can physically feel it well up in your lungs. I can feel the slow pressure build. There are so many mixed and varied emotions, joy, anger, excitment, dread. Nothing makes sense, everything is contradictory, yet they all are an equivalent. I think the strongest of my emotions or feelings would be my indecision....I keep writing things then deleting them. Words are tumbling out onto the tips of my fingers, spilling onto this empty page. I don't want to fill it up with the silly babble of a lost teenager...just like every other teenager trying to find her way in a world where nothing is right and so much is wrong.

I miss the firey heat of the sand under my feet as dance across the beach.

I miss the splash and crash of the waves with their white tips and their blue liquid.

I miss the crowd of umbrellas that were scattered across the sandy beach. All the colors blending together to make a mosiac collage of colors. 

I miss the sounds of the waves crashing and the seagulls calling out to their brothers.

I miss seeing the families and friends gathering, relaxing, and forgetting about all the responsiblities that would await them when they got home. 

I hated having to come home to the reality of the family and the small town.

I wanted to stay there forever and bask in the sun, feeling the heat soak into me like I was a sponge.

Still riding on the high that is called the beach. I can not wait because I will be there in 36 hours...that's awesome. 

I love God. I don't know why he has decided to touch me at this point in my life, but he makes me feel so happy and so loved, like nothing and no one else could. 

It's weird, sometimes when I get ready to go to sleep, my lips start to tingle and I can feel the blood rushing to my lips. They want to be kissed. It's not me, it's my lips!

I am living up this last month before school. I am trying to get as many of my days filled with friends and family...more friends than family though! 

Ever had a million things to say, but you are quite sure what they are?

Not only CAN I, but I WILL

The beach is calling out my name, and as the vaction draws nearer, I just try to behave more and more so God will let me have the best time ever! 

Oh thank goodness for the beach!

So what if it's an Ashlee Simpson song, if it speaks to ya, it speaks to ya!

Can you CRAVE a place? I crave the beach and I may bea ble to cure that craing. I want to go to the beach so bad and I think God knew that and he answered a prayer that I haven't even thought of asking. I am so excited about the beach...I don't care if there is an un-expected visitor...it will be okay because I want to be there so bad.

Tommorow is SAMM and COURTNEY day...we are going to go on a picnic..I am happy because I haven't hung out with her in like 2 weeks (a record for us)

Hope dangles on a string 
Like slow spinning redemption 
Winding in and winding out 
The shine of it has caught my eye

I always have fun at work when it's just me 'n the guys....it's a hoot. All of them gang up on me...and make me spectacular with their unorginal and clear flirting...lol...it's hilarious...


I am kinda happy the summer is almost gone....because that means my graduation date is growing closer....Ahh...I can smell the diploma already...Thank you GOD for college!!!!!!

It was so nice to see people other than my family or my co-workers. Going and hanging out, I forgot the pleasure in just awtching others bowl:) It makes me miss my friends less.

I <3 some Jesus. I am getting closer to God, kinda through my friend Madelyn, she makes me want to be a better person. She always has made me want to be better. I think that is just the effect she has on people :) MMMM...feels good to be a jesus freak!

Is it possible to be this bored and still have a pulse? I hate liveing on this side of town because all my friends live on the *other side of the tracks*! I get so tired of this house and this place. I think the walls could be moving in on me. I am excited about Senior year, although I feel like I am getting ready to go to college. Perhaps that is because I would rather be going to college. I am kinda 'cited about going to see Laura at VT once she gets settled in. She can show me a good time there, I can meet people that aren't from sucky Caroline! 

*I MISS ALL MY FRIENDS!!!!!!!*

Like whoa! It's been a long while.......

Saw him again yesterday....it's funny how everything comes back to him.

My mom is driving me nutz with her menapusel crap....but that's nothing new.

Soccer is much better this year. With two wins already on our back we are ready for the district games.

I can't wait till the beach and the concert. This is the best time of anyone's lives and I am finally living it up. It's about time!
I'm just tired of my mediocricy. I am so mediocore, I can't spell it. Everything points to my easy replacable-ness. I guess I should just accept it.

These past few weeks have flown by in such a slow procession I think sometimes everything is going backwards. A range of feelings have lifted me and up and brought me down. Treacherous ideas have filled my thoughts while, simple incidents have been over looked. I think I have over thought some things at the same time. So many things I fear may happen that I have become more timid than I ever have been. Fear chases my courage and my courage is becoming tired. I am not sure what is fueling this fear so much that it is able to over run my courage, but I must cut this source of fuel off. I fear that I may lose my position as goalie. I fear that people will just think of me as mean, even though I really am not that mean. I fear that I will chicken out on everything and take no chances and live in a safe world with all the same old scenarios. There will be no explosions here. I want something unusual something strange to call me to something exciting. 

Then there is my church which has fallen to the devil's grasp. That is the one safe place that I am supposed to be able to mmet God, but everything has changed there now. i don't think i can go back and that saddens me. I feel over run with thoughts and these thought may over run me because I am losing my strength and as my lose my strength those thoughts only go stronger.

I am no saint

Sometimes it becomes tiresome to wake up. I know that sounds bad, but I am still waiting for that good thing to happen to me. It just pray that today is as bad as it gets. I guess I am tired of everyone thinking I'm mean. Things seem to fall apart at the seams, both literally and figuratively. I guess I just need some space from all the people. Some space to be me, to be a happier version of me. Accepting the fact that bad things happen to good people could most possibly the most difficult thing ever.


I just want to send a congrats to my running buddies! Great Job people....good luck at Regionals!

The day was normal
Everything was okay
Until 9:47
That's when I got the call
The call that would keep me up for a while
The call that is now having me listen to old school MANDY MOORE...the sad stuff
Tired of the sad stuff...
I was getting strong
Did he sense that?
I wonder if three in the morning I will be thinking about you again
Is this some sick game that I am playing
I don't want to walk home alone anymore
I don't want to write depressing stuff.
Gimme something to smile about.
Snow days
Friends who make you smile.
He makes me smile sometimes too...wait...no...we must not think of that.



My sister saw me talking to him on the phone and said, "I thought you hated him?" 
I could only say "I don't know what I think or want anymore."

I try but I can't seem to get myself to think of anything but you.
I wanna be with you, if only for one night. To be the one who is in your arms and hold you tight. I wanna be with you there's nothing more to say there's nothing more that I want than to not feel this way.

Every thing seems to be so screwy

Why is simplicity so often over-looked?

Why don't things ever come out of my mouth the way that they are formulated in my head?

I have been listenin' to these three songs all day.

"I am heaven sent, don't you dare forget. I am all you ever wanted, what all the other boys promised." ---Brand New
 
"And I hope that all is well in heaven, cuz it's so shot to hell down here." ---Yellow Card

"If it makes you less sad, I will die by your hand." ---Brand New

I like being told I am spiffy. 

I like seeing someone who reminds me of summer when I am in the bitter cold.

I like putting my pictures on my http://desperately.deviantart.com page

I like you and I hope you like me to
I mean why wouldn't you?

I just realized, thanks to a rather nice fella, what I have been lacking these past few months. I have lacked inspiration. I got so focused on just getting everything done and getting it done right and just going going going, I have lost my need for inspiration.
  
   Those beautiful things that just make life worth living, those are the things I have been missing out on. With soccer starting back up soon, I know that will only add to my inspiration because of my pure love of the sport. Will that be enough though? I fearfully doubt it. 
   
   I guess I want more of a BIG BANG inspiration. Something to just wonderfully slide into my life like it was always just meant to be there. I think I need to get back to me. As much as I want everyone else to be right and everything else to be right....I think right now I just need to be alright. And you know what, I will be alright....because I am already feeling a lil inspired



(P.S. this isn't just another whoa is me i don't have a guy crap...this exceeds far beyond that)

He laughed at me today. 
I was walking to class and he greeted me...smug and sarcastic and then he laughed. 
Then his friends joined in. 
My head was already low, but it hung even lower.
I then passed humiliation into anger.
Fierce anger, I began throwing up the ball and punching it with all my might. 
Tears were held at bay by strength and will.
I refused to cry anymore.
I want to cry now.
That's the stage I am in. 
Can I cry now?

A new year is approaching
I don't think to much will change

I resolve to forget a little easier. 

I resolve to belive a little more.

While looking at a Magaizine I opened to "The New Year Do's & Don'ts".

The first one I see is:
"Do resolve to not fall in love with someone who isn't also intrested in you."

I deleted it all.

It's like a lost memory, or so I wished.

There's no trace of you except those few numbers.

I haven't the will power to delete those yet.

But I will.

Soon enough I will have deleted it all.

Actually while in Minnesota I had quite the few reminders that I wasn't such a bad catch and that if I wanted to I could prolly get a decent guy.....but what's the fun with trying? I just need help remebering that I am a great gal and if you can't see it, then you are missing out.


"Turn around walk away make it easier no one is forcing you to stay make it easier you stole my past I want it back dont' let the door hit your ass.....screw hello you had me at goodbye

So I wake up this morning, the first and not last mistake of the day. I am packing getting ready to leave from Nebraska and I pick up my phone and I get the urge to text Matt....so I listen to that little voice. I say What if? No not to mysef, that's what I text to Matt, "What if" He only replies with a ? so I reply to THAT with what if it is all lies. Once again his only reply was ?, So I get bol;d and listen to that voice in my head saying, stop locking it up, get it over with it, it can't hurt to actually hear the truth. So I tect, "What if I like you!" Well I push send,buyt halfway through the sending process I chicken out and cancel it, or so I thought. Suddenly...*BEEP BEEP* DELIVERED

SHIT.....THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING.....
The dreaded reply: That what if....

Wait...that sounds positivee....shut up...nuh uh....I say ?
Then the REAL dreaeded reply..........

"Honestly right now I don't even have time 4 myself let alone ne 1 else. alwys workn & school I only have 1 day off a week & its usualy 4 homework Wouldn't be fair"


I LAUGH....AND LAUGH....I JUST GOT PASSED UP FOR HOMEWORK...RICH....
I tell hinm there's no need for excuses and just say he doesn't like me

It would make it easier on me if he had just said he didn't like me, b/c that makes it weasier to walk away once and for all. CLOSE MY EYES TO IT ALL AND SHUT THE DOOR. But like YC says, "It only gets harder the more you know" Because time ceases and time sometimes leave openings.....just tell me you hate call me rude things make it easy to walk away......

Is it wrong to want to have a fling? Just to feel another's heart beat against your own? To feel the warm blood run through their lips, warming your own? Stretching up so you can look into someone's eyes seeing yourself, even though you know those aren't the eyes you want to see?

 

My lips quiver because they haven't been touched by anothers in so long. My hands shiver at the thought of holding someone else's. My legs shake because they can't stand the thought of having to stand alone once again through another year. My heart strings pull creating a melody that sounds so lonely even the love birds weep.

get you down too much.

Since when does Food Lion actually have cute employees? 

This guy's head prolly can't fit through door ways, but I mean it's not that hard to see why. His personality on the other hand is highly lacking. He has a very small one track mind, which is such a waste. He cracks me up though because he is slightly lacking on money so he is a Chip&Dale dancer. Yea, what a hoot! So where does he get off saying things like "Bye Beautiful". Good looking older guys don't say that stuff to me. He must not have gotten that memo. I don't want to be so shallow to say I am absolutely flattered, but I am absolutely flattered. I think I got it though, he knows ALREADY that I am a goody, which is good, cuz he knows I have boundaries. He must know that I would never actually be intrested in him bc all he is an exterior. He likes to chase things that he will never catch, a challenge for one. Well I am one challenge that most guys never pursue, so we will see how long it takes him to get bored. I hope it's soon, b.c. it's kinda freaky.....lol

You think I would be happy that a cute guy thinks I am pretty....but weirdly enough, it's more of a mystery.......

Life can be so funny sometimes.

I am so disdgusting when I am sick...
I stayed in the same clothes for like 24 hours
Didn't take a showerr for like 72 hours
Drank straight out of the orange juice container
Blew my nose like it was a saxaphone 
Let both the dogs sleep under the covers
let them lick my face because they thought that that was the best medicine

I sit down at the computers trying to stay away from you so Mad sits b.w. us. She logs on but all of sudden my computer doesn't work and the only one that is free is next to you. That's alrite though because I am strong enough to ignore your smell and refuse your smiles. What am I talking about after two minutes I can't help it, I have to touch you, just ruffle your hair, I need physical contact... you seem to be a mirage sometimes. You ask a favor and I know that there is no way I can say no not with that face shining at me. Mad tells me that you watch me walk away and I get giggly, I hate that you make me giggly, but not really, b/c sometimes it's good to feel giggly. I think that this might be what hell is like, continually being tortured by something you can't have. That only makes me want to be good so I won't ever have to know. 
Deep inside I keep looking for your imperfections picking through your exterior and interior, but I am so blinded that they are all hidden. I want to find something that I hate, b.c. that would make it so much easier. Your filling me to the rim and if I can't let this steam go I may explode....will you let me release it with you?

You are in my head and everytime I try and walk away I turn around and your there. There's nothing I can do to get away from you. 
I have tried I really have but when your face is etched on the inside of my eyelids what else can I expect.
I wake up thinking of you and wondering if you are thinking of me too.
I fall asleep hoping your dreams just might contain me.
My dreams revolve around you and your too perfect face that I can't hide from
I need to get away from this addictive drug and away from that of the flesh.
Rising above is what I need to do, but I don't know how when all I can think of is you.
(no intentional rhyming there)

I can't wait for Christmas, dunno why, but I just can't!

I hate trying to loose weight it is absolutely one of the most annoying things on this planet. I wish no one gained weight and we all had the perfect body types, because DAG IT...I WANT A COOKIE!
